data.description: Welcome to this spacious ranch home on a corner lot.  Lots of potential with this 4 bedroom 2 bath home.  Sits on 1 acre with a 3 car garage. Also has a breeze way when entering the home from the garage for more storage or potential working area.  Once inside you will notice a large kitchen, lving room, and spacious bedrooms with large closets.  Home has wood floors, and a walkout basement. The primary bedroom has a bonus area attached.  Hurry in to check this one out!
